        🔴📝 entanglement_storage ▶️🔧 implement_entanglement_based_storage quantum_superposition,
        🔴📝 quantum_compression ▶️🔧 add_quantum_data_compression entanglement_storage,
        🔴📝 supremacy_data ▶️🔧 enable_quantum_supremacy_data_processing quantum_compression,

